# errors

**Instance Property**

A list of errors resulting from the coupon code update.

## Declaration

```swift
sequence <ApplePayError> errors;
```

## Discussion

List the errors in order of importance.

For information on the possible errors, see [doc://com.apple.applepayontheweb/documentation/ApplePayontheWeb/ApplePayError].

## Setting updated transaction details

- **newLineItems**: The list of updated line items incorporating the coupon code update.
- **newShippingMethods**: The list of available shipping methods.
- **newTotal**: The updated total resulting from the coupon code update.
